I"^<h2 id="pontifications">Pontifications</h2>

<p>aka how i recorded <a href="http://roland.micro.blog/2018/08/15/this-ones-for.html">this one’s for pat</a></p>

<ol>
  <li>record on <a href="https://instamic.io/pages/instamic-support-mobile-app">instaMic</a> which only records WAV files</li>
  <li>plug into Windows computer or mac  using USB (wireless would be better!)</li>
  <li>convert to mp3 with <a href="https://ffmpeg.zeranoe.com/builds/">ffmpeg</a></li>
  <li>upload with website to micro.blog</li>
</ol>

<ul>
  <li>here’s the ffmpeg command to convert WAV to mp3:</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> C:\Users\rtang\Documents\ffmpeg-20180815-4f8e65c-win64-static\bin\ffmpeg.exe -i D:\IST_0007.wav -f <span class="nb">mp
</span>3 hellopat.mp3
</code></pre></div></div>
